            - 2ndPlace Prize
            - Reliability
            - DR Points
        - Cost breakdown is put in expanable panel. 1st Place, 2nd Place, Contest Fee and Contest Total are always made visible.
        - Milestone bonus is shown only for Conceptualization contest.
        - A few text is also updated.
    Version 1.0.5 (Studio Contest Types - Release Assembly version 1.0) Change Notes:
        - For studio contest, For contest_fee, contestTypeId is used instead of id in the sub-type.
        - function loadContestFees, handleGetContestFeesByProject,getCurrentContestTypeXml is updated.
    @author pulky, snow01, waits
    @version 1.0.5
    @since 1.0
-->
